To run:

Create Python virtual environment:

$ virtualenv ~/virtualenvs/enviro-hack-charme/

Activate this Python in system path:

$ . ~/virtualenvs/enviro-hack-charme/bin/activate

Install Paster web application server
$ pip install PasteScript

Run application listening on port 8080
$ paster serve service.ini 

Load in browser

http://localhost:8080
